				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "A druid called Nettie poisoned us because she didn’t want to run the risk we’d turn into mind flayers and destroy the druid grove. With a lot of difficulty we managed to convince her to let us live and give us the antidote. After this scene, Gale is upset by what happened and he starts out being uncharacteristically angry."
